      "file_path": "robot/testsuites/demo.robot",
      "patchset_number": 3,
      "line": 33,
      "message": "Well, actually I wanted to separate this test case from \"normal\" one, because prior init testcase required user to pass openstack credentials for \"init\" to work successfully. For CNF use-cases there is no logical reason to provide any openstack parameters, that's why I separated it.\n\nIt also answers your question to my change in review https://gerrit.onap.org/r/#/c/testsuite/oom/+/96860/",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 5550,
